p: The woman put earplugs in.
p_translation: Аял кулагына  үндөн тоскучту тыгып койду.

p: I refilled my water bottle.
a1: I drank all the water in it.
a2: I kept it in the fridge.
p_translation: Мен  бөтөлкөмдү кайрадан суу менен толтурдум.

p: The television show was censored.
The ship wrecked.
The boy felt stumped by the riddle.
The phone rang.
a1: The man hung up the phone.
a2: The man picked up the phone.

p: The woman was staring at me.
The group left the museum.
a1: They took pictures of the exhibits.

p: The man started an argument with me.
a1: My friend introduced me to the man.
a2: My friend stood up for me.
p_translation: Ал киши мени менен талаша кетти.
a1_translation: Ал киши менен  досум мени тааныштырды.

p: The tire on my bike was flat.
a1: I pumped air into the tire.
a2: I switched gears on the bike.

p: The girl looked pale.
a1: Her father read her a story.
a2_translation: Атасы анын температурасы бар экенин байкады.

p: The pen ran out of ink.
The man was denied for a loan.
p_translation: Ал кишиге насыя берүүдөн баш тартышты.

p: The girl stayed home from school.
The trash bag was full.
a1: I took it to the dumpster.
a2: I dumped it down the sink.
a1_translation: Мен аны таштанды челекке алып бардым.

p: I vacuumed the carpet.
The man lost his temper.
a2: He threw a chair across the room.

p: The girl threw a twig into the campfire.
The man got out of the shower.
The parents wanted their children to go to college.
a1: They set aside a savings fund for tuition.
a2: They encouraged their children to play outside.
a1_translation: Алар окуу акысына үнөмдөө фондунан бөлүп беришкен.

p: The man unlaced his shoes.
The man ate half of the entree.
My ankle was swollen.
My office door was open.
a1: I talked to my colleague at my desk.
a2: I overheard the conversation in the hall.

p: I had to wait in line.
The man swatted at the fly.
The man wrote a will.
The runner sensed his competitor gaining on him.
a1: He dropped out of the race.
p_translation: Жөө күлүк атаандашынын ага жетейин деп калганын сезди.

p: I thought carefully about the problem.
a2: I came up with a solution.

p: The traveler walked on the shaky suspension bridge.
p_translation: Саякатчы солкулдаган асма көпүрөнү басып өттү.

p: The man anticipated the team's victory.
a1: He met his friends to watch the game.
a2: He made a bet with his friends.
a1_translation: Ал оюнду көрүү үчүн достору менен жолугушту.

p: The boy couldn't fall asleep.
